secondary_street_name: 28 Kirtling Street, 88 Kirtling Street and 2 Battersea Park Road
description: Non-Material Amendment to the outline planning permission dated the 5th December 2014 (ref: 2014/2837) for the restoration and redevelopment of Battersea Power Station and the surrounding land/sites. (The proposals update and amend the site-wide energy strategy, and replace a number of the approved drawings for the Power Station building itself following further detailed design development). The amendments include changes to the residential layouts and mix with 1 less unit; amendments to the layouts, north terrace, structural columns, slab levels, plant, office slot windows, atrium roof, service trench and an increase in cycle parking.
